name: Juggernaut
description:
Update: My First Baked VAE Version

I have tried several VAEs to see what would be the best fit for Juggernaut.

Since Juggernaut's focus is photography, I ultimately decided on the Tone Range Compressor VAE.

The softer contrast is perfect for photography. The whole thing works semi well in the artistic part.

If you're not satisfied, simply switch back to the original version 2.2.

I created the sample images this time using the "Euler" sampler to make it easier for you to recreate them.

Chillpixel's NinjaFix takes Stable Diffusion models to new heights, producing stunning visual art through precise neural network fine-tuning, improved accuracy, and stable output.

V2.2 was trained on additional 1,2k Images and 50k more Steps. So we are on about 130k steps so far :) . Output on Photorealism got a lot better in my opinion :)

If you want the NinjaFix with HiResFix (True Enhancer) on Juggernaut , then join Starship or Dreamwalker. If your PC Hardware isnt good enough (like mine :D ) then take a look at Starship :) Of course there are other models too ;)

The Examples are made with the 4xUltraSharp Upscaler .But of course you can also use other Upscale Versions

I would appreciate a review. And I'm also looking forward to seeing your images using this model :)

By the way, you can follow me on Instagram

Or you can buy me a Coffee/Beer (but it's really not necessary, I would still appreciate it though :D)
